Localization.Name: Avalos Scout Goggles (Modified)
Localization.Description: This version of Rambler's Avalos Scout goggles has been modified from its original form. Tech meets tough with the Avalos Scout goggles. Their unique and sturdy frame ensures that the lenses remain intact even after unexpected impacts or sudden atmospheric changes. Built for harsh environments but bold enough to be worn anywhere.
